Production: Principal photography took place in Santa Fe, New Mexico in December 2021. In February 2022, the film entered in post-production.
Release: In September 2023, Screen Media acquired all North American distribution rights and set a release for November 3, 2023, in the "top 10 markets".
Reception: On the review aggregator website Rotten Tomatoes, 17% of 6 critics' reviews are positive, with an average rating of 3.6/10.
